# ğŸš€ Node.js Express Starter (JWT + MySQL)

A **beginner-friendly Node.js project** built from scratch using **Express.js**.  
This project demonstrates **User CRUD operations**, **JWT-based authentication**, and **MySQL database integration**.

It is intended as a **learning reference** for developers who want to get started with **Node.js backend development** using real-world patterns.

